import React from 'react'
import {
    AboutMeContainer,
    AboutMeTop,
    AboutMeImgContainer,
    AboutMeImgBorder,
    AboutMeImage,
    AboutMeIntroContainer,
    AboutMeIntro,
    AboutMeOccupation,
} from './AboutMeElements'

const AboutMe = ({ img, intro, occupation }) => {
    return (
        <AboutMeContainer>
            <AboutMeTop>
                <AboutMeImgContainer>
                    <AboutMeImgBorder>
                        {/* <AboutMeImage alt="AboutMeImage" src={img} /> */}
                        HELLO
                    </AboutMeImgBorder>
                </AboutMeImgContainer>
                <AboutMeIntroContainer>
                    <AboutMeIntro>{intro}</AboutMeIntro>
                    <AboutMeOccupation>{occupation}</AboutMeOccupation>
                </AboutMeIntroContainer>
            </AboutMeTop>
        </AboutMeContainer>
    )
}

export default AboutMe
